{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaKeyMessageEvent()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent/MediaKeyMessageEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent\"><code>MediaKeyMessageEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>MediaKeyMessageEvent()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent/message\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent/messageType\"><code>messageType</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>MediaKeyMessageEvent</code></strong> constructor creates a new <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent\"><code>MediaKeyMessageEvent</code></a> object.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaKeyMessageEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaKeyMessageEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>type<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"type\"><code>type</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A string with the name of the event.\n      It is case-sensitive and browsers always set it to <code>message</code>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"options\"><code>options</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An object that, <em>in addition of the properties defined in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\" title=\"Event()\"><code>Event()</code></a></em>, can have the following properties:</p>\n    <dl>\n      <dt id=\"messagetype\"><code>messageType</code></dt>\n      <dd>\n        <p>\n          A message type that allows applications to differentiate messages without parsing them.\n          Allowed values are: <code>license-request</code>, <code>license-renewal</code>, <code>license-renewal</code>, or <code>individualization-request</code>.\n        </p>\n      </dd>\n      <dt id=\"message\"><code>message</code></dt>\n      <dd>\n        <p>An array containing the message generated by the content decryption module.</p>\n      </dd>\n    </dl>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A new <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent\"><code>MediaKeyMessageEvent</code></a> object.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/encrypted-media/#constructors","title":"Encrypted Media Extensions"}],"query":"api.MediaKeyMessageEvent.MediaKeyMessageEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaKeyMessageEvent.MediaKeyMessageEvent","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent/MediaKeyMessageEvent/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The MediaKeyMessageEvent constructor creates a new MediaKeyMessageEvent object.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-06-01T05:12:48.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/mediakeymessageevent/mediakeymessageevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/mediakeymessageevent/mediakeymessageevent/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/c1f8207fa145db27da55bf832c85a63aeb7d24b7","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent","title":"MediaKeyMessageEvent"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaKeyMessageEvent/MediaKeyMessageEvent","title":"MediaKeyMessageEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"MediaKeyMessageEvent() - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}